<item>
            <title>[LU-15634] Use after free in ptlrpc</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15634</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ptlrpc: Use after free of &apos;conn&apos; in rhashtable retry&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Use after free of &apos;conn&apos; in the uncommon case of&lt;br/&gt;
rhashtable_lookup_get_insert_fast failing with -EBUSY or -ENOMEM&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Move OBD_FREE_PTR(conn) below the retry and set conn2 to NULL&lt;br/&gt;
on error, propagating to conn and returning to the caller.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fixes: 37b29a8f70 (&quot;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8130&quot; title=&quot;Migrate from libcfs hash to rhashtable&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-8130&quot;&gt;LU-8130&lt;/a&gt; ptlrpc: convert conn_hash to rhashtable&quot;);&lt;/p&gt;</description>
